# ThejaD (mandatory)

## Unlock (persistent)

- **Maximum:** MCP `thejad_unlock` phrase `mamaThejana` — stays at **100%** until you lock.
- **Lock:** MCP `thejad_unlock` phrase `nothejad unlock` (or type that exact text in chat).

## Auto-orchestra (no MCP call needed)

Cursor hooks run on **every user message**:

1. `beforeSubmitPrompt` → ThejaD orchestra + models + role/skills
2. Result written to **`.thejad/last-orchestra.md`**
3. Read that file and **execute the optimized prompt** — do not call `thejad_orchestrate` again unless the hook failed.

`sessionStart` injects tier + setup state.

## First machine setup

`thejad_setup_status` → user logins/env → `thejad_setup_complete` (or `thejad init` auto-completes when Ollama + repo OK).

## Env (`.cursor/mcp.json` → ThejaD)

`FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN`, `FIGMA_FILE_URL`, `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `THEJAD_DEVICE_ROOTS`, `THEJAD_HOOK_FAST=1` (faster hooks, skip Ollama warm).

## Team pod (LAN + Hyperspace-class)

1. MCP **`thejad_pod_init`** on each device on the same network  
2. On each device: **`node thejad/bin/thejad.js pod serve`** (port 19090)  
3. MCP **`thejad_pod_peer_add`** with peer URLs `http://<IP>:19090`  
4. **`thejad_pod_memory_sync`** — shared memory across all agents  
5. **`thejad_agent_manifest_export`** / **`apply`** — same agent level for every user  
6. Optional full stack: [pods.hyper.space](https://pods.hyper.space/) — set `HYPERSPACE_GATEWAY_URL` + `HYPERSPACE_POD_API_KEY`  

Phase 1 only · **Thanks to Theja**
